#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.kmouth.appdata.xml:9
msgid ""
"KMouth is a program which enables persons that cannot speak to let their "
"computer speak, e.g. mute people or people who have lost their voice. It has "
"a text input field and speaks the sentences that you enter. It also has "
"support for user defined phrasebooks."
msgstr ""
"KMouth je program, ki omogoča osebam, ki ne morejo govoriti kot npr. nemi "
"ljudje ali ljudje, ki so izgubili glas, da njihov računalnik govori namesto "
"njih.  Ima polje za vnos besedila in govori stavke, ki jih vnesete. Prav "
"tako ima podporo za uporabniško določene zbirke fraz. Opomba prevajalca: "
"zaenkrat je podprt samo angleški generator govora."
